data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:GameStop;elmt:;cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=ffe106af-8248-4af3-9098-a2d4fd637766&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=GameStop&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiJmZmUxMDZhZi04MjQ4LTRhZjMtOTA5OC1hMmQ0ZmQ2Mzc3NjYiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZ2FtZXN0b3AuY29tL3N0ZWFtLWRlY2stbGF1bmNoLWxvY2F0b3IuaHRtbCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNTUyZmJmMGItNmIzYS00YjdmLWEyNTAtOTY4YWI2NTY3NzdkIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAdIo1xfFqczuRbuezbRzncdQ4OsUSmkWIzSB0EfD_C_9&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamestop.com%2Fsteam-deck-launch-locator.html" class="rapid-with-clickid">GameStop 翻新的 Steam Decks</a>也于今日上市。它们在指定零售店以“比新型号便宜 20%”的价格出售，并且仅面向拥有 GameStop Pro 会员资格的客户提供，年费为 25 美元。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/valve-begins- sell-refurbished-steam-decks-for-around-20-percent-off-201808966.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/valve-begins-selling-refurbished-steam-decks-for-around-20-percent-off-201808966.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 552fbf0b-6b3a-4b7f-a250-968ab656777d</guid><dc:creator>威尔·尚克林</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 08 Aug 2023 20:18:08 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691524994</ingested><modified> 2023-08-08T20:03:17+00:00</modified><category><![CDATA[Professional Services]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="984" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/b7f84340-3623-11ee-97a5-d5901c5355a1" width="1750"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></med