l"><ins>试图让苹果支持 RCS，但没有成功</ins></a>，但后者对使用自己的 iMessage 服务进行加密消息感到<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tim-cook-response-green-bubbles-android-your-mom-095538175.html"><ins>非常满意</ins></a>。因此，只有当您的群组中的每个成员都使用 Android 或 iOS 设备时，您才能够接受 E2EE 聊天，除非您选择使用<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/signal/"><ins>Signal</ins></a>等第三方应用程序。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/google-says-all-group-rcs-chats-are-now-filled-end-to-end-encrypted-200337049.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/google-says-all-group-rcs-chats-are-now-fully-end-to-end-encrypted-200337049.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 976535f5-ec05-4b47-91e3-0f07cce67832</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 08 Aug 2023 20:03:37 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691525018</ingested><modified> 2023-08-08T20:03:43+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="3761" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-images/2020-02/c22eb980-521e-11ea-bb87-d7f01043e879" width="5642"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3761" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-images/2020-02/c22eb980-521e-11ea-bb87-d7f01043e879" width="5642"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]